{"tid":1649465,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【抗暴之戰●沙田】陶輝現身沙田站！肩章變助理處長階級徽章","createTime":"2019-10-12T16:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T19:14:38.000Z","uid":244704,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1ba213ebd74644fab433429786ede381bad5adc9","tid":1649465,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191012/large/1570892276_8036.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191012%2Flarge%2F1570892276_8036.jpg&h=38e8930b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n逆權運動逾4個月，警方拘捕約2,400人，開實彈槍漸成常態，其中在6.12警察暴力清場中，被指指揮鎮壓的英籍指揮官陶輝（Rupert Dover）亦為最令人熟悉的警察。陶輝在運動初時，經常出現在大大小小的示威場合，惟去到運動中期已沒有出現，至今晚，久未露面的陶輝終於出現在新城市廣場內，但《蘋果》記者在現場發現，其肩章竟已變成助理處長階級徽章。 <br />\n<br />\n晚上9時許，十多名身穿黑衣的男子破壞沙田站後火速離開，未幾大批防暴警及消防到場戒備。大約半小時後，身穿防暴裝備的陶輝亦在3名防暴警的陪同下到沙田站了解，他未有回應在場記者的提問，經過閘機進入沙田站的控制室。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》現場所見，陶輝所穿的制服上，其肩章變成「警務處助理處長階級徽章」，記者亦在政府電話簿內，發現陶輝的官階為「署理新界南總區指揮官」。有網民懷疑陶輝是否因鎮壓多次衝突而升職，但有消息指，由於現任新界南總區指揮官黎德禮在多月前因病休假，陶輝才會成為署理新界南總區指揮官。"},{"pid":"d3c280eab0bcf4241494d95c28d22a55aedd4b9f","tid":1649465,"uid":113200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BcS0VdB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBcS0VdB.jpg&h=fbe211c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Th5mEFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTh5mEFh.jpg&h=fe366e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HY70VdC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHY70VdC.jpg&h=f30d17b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T80UZFk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT80UZFk.png&h=d8015181&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f41c8f22417b240d394186ab837c6ea03833f58a","tid":1649465,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:18:39.000Z","msg":"［核彈行動］令警察家變！針對警妻開闢新文宣線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647500</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳情請睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647500</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0403fa50d2c166036ee1599cf8a8aefe835fbb50","tid":1649465,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ed3419ef23e324e65b97b19d0f3c7cc3013700f0","tid":1649465,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:10:57.000Z","msg":"呢隻賤種要佢留係大陸"},{"pid":"fca8b51ece6be0a5463c0c529419709434819ed5","tid":1649465,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:28:38.000Z","msg":"死鬼頭黎德禮病左三個月<br />\n係咪死撚左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【逃犯條例．Emily Online】清場指揮官陶輝升職？ (18:14) 2019/7/16<br />\n<br />\n警方新界南總區應變大隊外籍總警司陶輝（Rupert Dover），一直被指有份喺6月12日金鐘清場行動中下令向示威者開槍。有眼利網民喺連登討論區發帖，話留意到上星期日九龍大遊行期間，陶輝膊頭官階仲係總警司，呢個星期日喺沙田清場期間已經變咗助理處長，仲質疑佢點解咁快升咗職。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEmily查返政府電話簿，見到本身係新界南總區副指揮官嘅陶輝，𠵱家身兼署理新界南總區指揮官。Emily就問過警方消息人士，佢就話原本新界南總區指揮官黎德禮（Patrick Laidler），因為身體抱恙請咗病假，由陶輝署任住先。查實警方高層升職信（yes letter）通常都係年尾派發，消息人士就話，上年年尾升職信就未見有陶輝份。不過陶輝咁積極參與「踏浪者行動」（Operation Tiderider），今年年尾會唔會更上一層樓、坐正做助理處長，我諗Emily同好多網民都好關心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190716/s00001/1563270920956/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-emily-online%E3%80%91%E6%B8%85%E5%A0%B4%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE%E5%AE%98%E9%99%B6%E8%BC%9D%E5%8D%87%E8%81%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190716%2Fs00001%2F1563270920956%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-emily-online%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B8%2585%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258F%25AE%25E5%25AE%2598%25E9%2599%25B6%25E8%25BC%259D%25E5%258D%2587%25E8%2581%25B7&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9qZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=534331b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190716%2Fs00001%2F1563270920956%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-emily-online%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B8%2585%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258F%25AE%25E5%25AE%2598%25E9%2599%25B6%25E8%25BC%259D%25E5%258D%2587%25E8%2581%25B7&h=74e7016c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190716/s00001/1563270920956/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-emily-online%E3%80%91%E6%B8%85%E5%A0%B4%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE%E5%AE%98%E9%99%B6%E8%BC%9D%E5%8D%87%E8%81%B7</a>"},{"pid":"64adc72b16c9932370a5d8ad11b3f2b195576732","tid":1649465,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:14:38.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}